      "source": [
        "This is an exploration of whether logistic regression, random forest or mlp is better for an IDS system.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Why was each chosen**\n",
        "\n",
        "*Logistic Regression*\n",
        "\n",
        "Logistic regression is a simple classical machine learning model that serves as a baseline to test other machine learning and deep learning models against.\n",
        "\n",
        "*Random forest*\n",
        "\n",
        "Random forest is a complicated machine learning model that works well with noisy and small datasets. This is used to test how well machine learning would work for an IDS.\n",
        "\n",
        "*Multilayer perceptron (MLP)*\n",
        "\n",
        "MLP is a basic deep learning model that works well for complicated patterns and can process very large amounts of data well. This is used as a test to differentiate between machine learning and deep learning for an IDS."
      ],
